aim_flashbang

Created For CS Source by SolidSnakes
chris@battlefield.co.nz

Terrorist: Kill CT With Flashbangs
Counter-Terrorist: Kill T With Flashbangs

You are slapped to two health at the start.
Your objective is to kill each other with,
_ONLY_ flashbangs.

There is a secret in the map...
See if you can find it :)

Enjoy....
